\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The domain of the log-normal distribution is restricted to positive values.
 If,
 for a particular technology,
 the costs of energy input in production (
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{e}uTE_{l,e}\cdot pTE_{e}$
\end_inset

) exceed the marginal price of energy 
\begin_inset Formula $pES^{marg}$
\end_inset

